WEBVTT

00:03.430 --> 00:09.240
Qualcomm's Snapdragon chipset solutions enable some of the industry's...

00:09.500 --> 00:12.540
...most powerful smartphones on the market today.

00:12.740 --> 00:20.620
This is why, we say that inside today's smartest devices beats the heart of a dragon.

00:21.650 --> 00:28.820
But we cannot bestow the heart of a dragon without first learning what that truly means.

00:28.960 --> 00:34.660
Thus, Qualcomm has created the Way of the Dragon retreat,...

00:34.800 --> 00:41.700
...so that we all may become one with the closest thing on Earth to a true dragon,...

00:42.270 --> 00:43.970
...Komodo dragons.

00:44.570 --> 00:52.310
These creatures know all the truth of the universe if we simply choose to listen.

00:53.050 --> 00:59.120
Our innovative training with Komodo dragons makes Qualcomm engineers...

00:59.250 --> 01:04.190
...more alert, more awake, more attuned to their essence.

01:04.760 --> 01:06.960
It's an innovative approach that helps our engineers...

01:07.100 --> 01:10.470
...develop new levels of creativity and ingenuity when faced with challenges.

01:11.670 --> 01:13.840
Komodo dragons help us see new possibilities,...

01:14.570 --> 01:18.140
...and I think that's reflected by the fact that Snapdragon is the best chipset on the market.

01:19.010 --> 01:25.780
For more information, please visit facebook.com/qualcomm.

